B.Tc=new A.d0("A qualifier was added to the lifetime cover headline","The unconditional wording sets an expectation the policy can't always keep, and pre-existing exclusions are the most common reason a claim is declined.",'Something like "subject to your pet\'s health history" keeps it accurate without changing the meaning for most customers. Flagged to copy and compliance.',B.k9)
