B.Ua=new A.bO("Lead with value, not forms","The onboarding experiences I admired, Biscuit among them, explained what the product would do for you before asking anything of you.")
B.TR=new A.bO("Short, visual sequences beat long forms","Feature carousels and progress indicators were consistently tied to higher engagement and lower drop-off than text-heavy, question-first flows.")
B.U5=new A.bO("Be explicit about what\u2019s optional","The best examples were clear about what was required, what was optional, and, most importantly, why each piece of information was being asked for.")
